政府不全面回應市民訴求，亦不明白政府為何斟酌用字，迴避用「撤回」一詞。"},{"pid":"b22d2ae1c1b0f6debaea051d596cab078812cea3","tid":1302539,"uid":92439,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"觀瑪仔敢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c5024fe5c8e2d9d6487597258aa31f8c209bf1","tid":1302539,"uid":34777,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"呢啲先叫狀元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係叫你話一定要喺鏡頭前大大力屌政府<br />\n只係想你真係講番啲人話<br />\n呢啲咪做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72e63513f4c40b71939e6b61be874dc0ac3676b","tid":1302539,"uid":80371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"觀瑪仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77beec54dc981092d61ff773ab5a1b13f8160a4a","tid":1302539,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"鮮海行果條友係咪份左呢間"},{"pid":"b229905d5755f3fe8c841b91ff28113931ea0999","tid":1302539,"uid":80371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77beec54dc981092d61ff773ab5a1b13f8160a4a","tid":1302539,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"鮮海行果條友係咪份左呢間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"df0df5a9cd1a96574031692e908703e18300a820","tid":1302539,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"觀瑪仔！"},{"pid":"f02b1a5bffd0cc8381d904d68e908b7cb621b65b","tid":1302539,"uid":80371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\